<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Overswear" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Overswear,</orth> to swear again: <cit><quote>all those sayings will I o.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 5.276" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 276</bibl></cit>. cf. <emph>swear over</emph> in <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.424" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 424</bibl> (== to swear down, to bear down with swearing).
